opinions.text:
ORDER
The plaintiff’s motion to affirm the judgment of the Superior Court pursuant to Rule 16(g) is denied.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Dennis H. Esposito, Providence, for plaintiff.
Quinn, Cuzzone & Geremia, John F. Cuz-zone, Jr., Providence, for defendant.
